                </p>
                <p>
                    <span>Géraldine Gavard</span>
                    <i>Sales director,
                        <a href="http://www.lepatriarche.com/en/index_en.html" target="_blank">Restaurant Le
                            Patriarche
                        </a>
                    </i>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span>Roger Pichette</span>
                    <b>National Vice President, JCI Canada &amp; Entertainment committee</b>
                    <i>Lawyer,
                        <a href="http://www.bernierbeaudry.com/" target="_blank">Bernier Beaudry inc.</a>
                    </i>
                </p>
                <h2 class="{res.style.round}">Finances and Sponsors</h2>
                <p>
                    <span>Martin Côté</span>
                    <b>Director, sponsors</b>
                    <i>Mortgage specialist,
                        <a href="http://www.tdcanadatrust.com/" target="_blank">TD Canada Trust</a>
                    </i>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span>Pierre-Yves Dubois</span>
                    <b>Director, finances</b>
                    <i>Tax manager,
                        <a href="http://www.deloitte.com/" target="_blank">Deloitte s.e.n.c.r.l</a>
                    </i>
                </p>
                <h2 class="{res.style.round}">Formal events and Logistics</h2>
                <p>
                    <span>Rudy Boutet</span>
